
ip
	UTIL part of 'iproute2' (just iproute under Debian)
	for 2.2 & up kernels
	can supercede ifconfig, route, arp, though essential when > 1 route
	some criticism of these that report format not as clear as earlier tools


show all links & addresses
	link show	like ipconfig
	ip address show

show routing
	route show
	ip route ls dev ethX

